Package: cronR
Type: Package
Title: A package for interacting with cron jobs from R.
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2013-11-23
Author: Kevin Ushey
Maintainer: Kevin Ushey <kevinushey@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows you to create, edit, and remove cron
    jobs on your unix-alike system. It provides a set of easy-to-use wrappers
    to crontab.
Imports:
    digest
License: MIT + file LICENSE
SystemRequirements: cron
